summary: This Tweet is partially true, but misleading. A look at the city archives shows that the image in the Tweet actually comes from a planned april fools day prank.    Here’s the city hall press release in the archives: http://officialsource...
This is an actual photo, but from an April Fools day joke the city played last year. No sparkling water soon. See the city paper’s coverage of the joke: http://localnewssource...
